 "lrc": "[00:00.00]Ads in the cracks, brands in the chat\n[00:02.77]Everybody got stats, everybody wants claps\n[00:11.04]Everybody got reach but don't reach back\n[00:14.40]How we got this close and lost contact?\n[00:15.20]You can see me in a second\n[00:16.48]You can call me any day\n[00:19.20]You can love me in private\n[00:20.00]But scroll right past my name\n[00:48.96]Funny how we got connected\n[00:52.48]Then forgot how to stay\n[00:52.48]You're right there in my pocket\n[00:52.48]But you feel a world away\n[00:52.48]One tap away (one tap away)\n[00:56.77]From a real conversation but we don't say a thing\n[01:05.76]We're one tap away\n[01:07.32]From \"I see you keep going\" from \"I'm proud of your dream\"\n[01:10.73]Save your likes for the strangers\n[01:13.12]Save your hearts for the stars\n[01:15.76]But the ones who really know you act like loving you is hard\n[01:20.16]One tap away\n[01:20.96]So why do I feel alone in a room full of names?\n[01:26.16]Tap, tap, but you don't reach back\n[01:28.40]Heart, heart, but it don't feel like that\n[01:30.88]Close, close, close, but we don't connect\n[01:33.84]One tap away and we still forget\n[01:36.00]Click, click, click, everybody got a new rule\n[01:38.72]Don't hype friends that ain't cool, cool\n[01:41.60]Save that love for the big names\n[01:43.44]Blue checks, big chains, big views\n[01:45.92]That if a stranger blow up overnight\n[01:49.12]Everybody's where they saw the light\n[01:50.80]Same ones quiet when you need a find\n[01:53.12]Now they in the comments like \"that's my guy\"\n[01:55.84]One tap away\n[01:58.80]And still so far\n[02:00.08]Everybody online\n[02:00.64]Nobody where you are\n"
